document_data.mainbody:
'''"Menace of the Icy Spire"''' is a short adventure for [[Dungeons & Dragons]] 4{{th}} edition published in [[Dungeon magazine 159|''Dungeon'' #159]].
{{TOC limit|2}}
{{Quote|''"MENACE OF THE ICY SPIRE" is a Dᴜɴɢᴇᴏɴs & Dʀᴀɢᴏɴs® adventure for five characters of 2nd level. The adventure is set in the Fᴏʀɢᴏᴛᴛᴇɴ Rᴇᴀʟᴍs® setting near the town of Loudwater in the Gray Vale. This adventure is designed to work well with the sample adventures found in Chapter 1 of the ''Fᴏʀɢᴏᴛᴛᴇɴ Rᴇᴀʟᴍs Campaign Guide''. In particular, this adventure makes an excellent sequel to ''Barrow of the Ogre King'', which introduces Loudwater and the surrounding area along with several NPCs who would make ideal patrons for sending the PCs on this adventure. However, it is not necessary for the characters to have visited Loudwater previously.''}}

